TI  - ASSESSMENT OF COASTAL VULNERABILITY TO SEA LEVEL RISE USING REMOTE SENSING (RS) AND GEOGRAPHIC INFORMATION SYSTEMS (GIS): A CASE STUDY OF BOLINAO, PANGASINAN, PHILIPPINES
JO  - NANA
PY  - 2012
